column4: The awarded loans will settle on November 20, 2008, and will mature on December 18, 2008. The stop-out rate shown above will apply to all awarded loans.
column5: Institutions that submitted winning bids will be contacted by their respective Reserve Banks by 11:30 a.m. EST on November 18, 2008. Participants have until 12:30 p.m. EST on November 18, 2008, to inform their local Reserve Bank of any error.
